| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-1242 — Recovery Inhibition (dispossessor)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 3bd27a2d-e6d9-501f-9a65-c055b8596ea1"
